Comment: 0,0:01:23.98,0:01:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,------------------------------OP「Now On Air」----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.27,0:01:27.82,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢の続きをリライト
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.82,0:01:31.20,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}聞こえますか？未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:36.58,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}君と声を重ねて届ける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.58,0:01:45.34,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}はじまりのナンバー　夢にとどけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.34,0:01:50.47,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}平坦な道　探して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.47,0:01:53.76,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}進むことに飽きたの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.76,0:01:56.76,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}叶えても　叶うだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:02:01.73,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢はなぜこの手で　形を変えてくの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.73,0:02:07.77,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}教えて　どれくらい？　頑張れば辿り着くの…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.77,0:02:13.07,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}理想につぶれてた　私はもういない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.45,0:02:16.53,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢の先をリライト
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.53,0:02:19.74,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}掴みたいよ未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:27.13,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}君と声を重ねて　届けるの　もっと先へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.13,0:02:30.21,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}ひとりじゃ歩けない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:33.38,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}景色　君とみてみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:36.68,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}ひとりじゃ進めない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.68,0:02:39.31,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}直感を信じて生きてたい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.31,0:02:42.39,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢の先の New World
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:45.65,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}聞こえていますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.65,0:02:49.57,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}この声が終わるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.57,0:02:53.44,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}君に伝え続けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.27,0:01:27.82,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}重写梦想的续集
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.82,0:01:31.20,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}会听到未来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:36.58,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}我们的声音重叠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.58,0:01:45.34,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}送出的开场曲 飞向梦想吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.34,0:01:50.47,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}总是寻找平坦的路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.47,0:01:53.76,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}只会让我厌倦前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.76,0:01:56.76,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}就算去实现 也只是完成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:02:01.73,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}梦想为何会因为这只手改变形态呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.73,0:02:07.77,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}请告诉我 还要努力多久才能到达
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.77,0:02:13.07,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}曾经只能仰视理想的我 已经改变
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.45,0:02:16.53,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}重写梦想的延续
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.53,0:02:19.74,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}希望把握住未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:27.13,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}我们的声音重叠 直抵更远方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.13,0:02:30.21,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}一个人走不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:33.38,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}想和你一同欣赏美景
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:36.68,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}一个人无法前进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.68,0:02:39.31,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}希望能追随直觉活着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.31,0:02:42.39,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}梦想前方的新世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:45.65,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}你听清楚了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.65,0:02:49.57,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}直到无法发声为止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.57,0:02:53.44,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}我都会一直为你开口
Comment: 0,0:22:10.02,0:22:13.19,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,---------------------------ED「STAND BY YOU」------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.19,0:22:18.57,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}Stand by me, you did that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.57,0:22:21.20,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}Stand by you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.41,0:22:31.12,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}気持ち伝えるのにいつも何故　こんなにも悩み
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.12,0:22:34.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}ゆらり揺れている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.29,0:22:41.05,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}本当は君が好きなのに　うらはらで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.05,0:22:44.72,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}上手く言えないよ　ねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.64,0:22:47.43,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}振り返れば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.89,0:22:50.60,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}君が映る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.68,0:22:54.35,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}目と目合わせ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.35,0:22:59.44,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}愛の歌　そう唄い出す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:05.66,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}君にいつか届くまでね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.66,0:23:08.24,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}大事にしてたフィーリング
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.24,0:23:10.70,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}全部込めるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.70,0:23:15.71,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}ちゃんと受け止めてくれるよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.71,0:23:20.96,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}真夜中のラブソングで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.96,0:23:26.93,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}世界がちょっと変わってほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.93,0:23:32.31,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}そして君とsweetie　2人ぼっち
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.31,0:23:34.98,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}100ミリちょっとの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.98,0:23:37.06,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}隙間埋める
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.06,0:23:38.90,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}be with you
Comment: 0,0:22:13.19,0:22:18.57,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,Stand by me, you did that
Comment: 0,0:22:18.57,0:22:21.20,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,Stand by you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.41,0:22:31.12,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}只是表明心意 为什么让我如此烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.12,0:22:34.29,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}总是摇摆不定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.29,0:22:41.05,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}其实那么喜欢你 却言不由衷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.05,0:22:44.72,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}找不到合适的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.64,0:22:47.43,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}回首身后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.89,0:22:50.60,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}眼中有了你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.68,0:22:54.35,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}我们四目相对
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.35,0:22:59.44,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}唱响这首爱之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:05.66,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}希望有一天你能听到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.66,0:23:08.24,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}一直珍惜的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.24,0:23:10.70,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}都包含其中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.70,0:23:15.71,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}你一定会接受它吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.71,0:23:20.96,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}愿这首午夜小情歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.96,0:23:26.93,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}可以让世界稍微改变
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.93,0:23:32.31,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}然后与你甜甜蜜蜜 二人世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.31,0:23:34.98,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}十多厘米的间隙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.98,0:23:37.06,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}全都被填满
Comment: 0,0:23:37.06,0:23:38.90,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,be with you
